        <h1> Refund Policy</h1>


        <p> Thank you for choosing to be a part of the Malabar Literature Festival. We value your participation
          and
          support. Please read the following Refund Policy carefully before proceeding with your event
          registration, as it outlines the terms and conditions regarding refunds.</p>

        <h3> 1. Refund Policy Overview:</h3>
        <p>We understand that circumstances may change, and plans might need to be adjusted. However, kindly
          note
          that all event registrations made for the Malabar Literature Festival are non-refundable. This
          policy is
          in place to ensure the efficient organization and smooth execution of the festival.</p>

        <h3> 2. No Refund Policy:</h3>
        <p> Once an event registration is confirmed and payment is made, no refunds will be issued for any
          reason,
          including but not limited to, changes in personal schedules, travel arrangements, or any other
          unforeseen circumstances.</p>

        <h3> 3. Transferability:</h3>
        <p> Event registrations are non-transferable. This means that the registration cannot be transferred to
          another individual, event, or year.</p>

        <h3> 4. Event Changes or Cancellation:</h3>
        <p> In the unlikely event that the Malabar Literature Festival is canceled or rescheduled due to
          unforeseen
          circumstances, participants will have the option to either attend the rescheduled event (if
          applicable)
          or receive credit towards a future edition of the festival, as determined by the event organizers.
        </p>
        <h3> 5. Contact Information:</h3>
        <p>For any inquiries or assistance regarding your event registration, please contact our support team.
          We
          are here to help and address any concerns you may have.</p>

        <p> By proceeding with your event registration, you acknowledge and agree to abide by the terms and
          conditions outlined in this Refund Policy.</p>

        <p> Please ensure that you have reviewed all event details, dates, and schedules before finalizing your
          registration. We appreciate your understanding and cooperation in adhering to this policy.</p>

